<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="b1946_08_21_an_RebniAnna"><teiHeader><fileDesc> <titleStmt> <title>Von <persName key="WittgensteinLudwig" role="sender" full="yes">Ludwig Wittgenstein</persName> an <persName key="RebniAnna" role="recipient" full="yes">Anna Rebni</persName>, 21. 8. 1946</title> <author>Wittgenstein, Ludwig</author> </titleStmt> <publicationStmt> <p>Ludwig Wittgenstein: Gesamtbriefwechsel, 2. Auflage</p> </publicationStmt> <sourceDesc default="false"> <p>Abschrift (Norweger Briefe, S. 158). Publiziert (Norweger Briefe, S. 158).</p> </sourceDesc> </fileDesc><profileDesc> <creation>Brief geschrieben am 1946_08_21.</creation> </profileDesc><encodingDesc><p>TEI P5</p></encodingDesc><revisionDesc><list type="simple"><item>2007/06: Conversion from Folio Flat File to XML</item><item>2018/12: Added to Innsbruck Correspondence Edition</item></list></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div type="transcript" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"> <p rend="right">Frk. Anna Rebni </p> <p rend="right">Skjolden i Sogn </p> <p rend="right"><hi rend="underline">Norway </hi></p> <p>Dear Frk. Rebni,</p> <p rend="indent">Thank you for your letter which you gave Mr Richards for me. If you want to write to Marguerite Sjögren the best way is to write to her</p> <p rend="indent">c/o Hr Arvid Sjögren</p> <p rend="indent">15 Kornvægen</p> <p rend="indent">Stocksund</p> <p rend="indent">Sweden.</p> <p>Arvid Sjögren is her brother in-law &amp; will forward any post to her. He knows where she is at present.</p> <p rend="indent">All good wishes!</p> <p rend="indent">Yours sincerely</p> <p rend="right">Ludwig Wittgenstein</p> </div></body></text></TEI>